Insallation from SVN
====================

This project needs HDF5 version >= 1.8.2 . You can download it from
http://www.hdfgroup.org . After the installation of HDF5 proceed with the
following steps.


1. Checkout from SVN
--------------------

If not already done, checkout the SVN tree
# svn checkout http://svn.berlios.de/svnroot/repos/hdf5serie/trunk hdf5serie
OR
# svn checkout svn://svn.berlios.de/hdf5serie/trunk hdf5serie


2. Run AutoTools
----------------

# aclocal
# autoheader
# libtoolize -c --force
# autoconf
# automake -a -c --force


3. Proceed with configure
-------------------------

See file INSTALL.
